  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "After completing the Murder Tribunal trial and completing the Baptism of Blood, the Echo of Abazigal will appear in the courtroom to provide you with Bhaalist/assassiny wares. Abazigal was one of the Five Bhaalspawn from BG2: Throne of Bhaal.",
    "how_to_trigger": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A- Either complete the Baptism of Blood or use the Murder Tribunal's debugbook quest flags and options to become an Unholy Assassin and spawn the Murder Merchant.- The Echo of Abazigal will appear in the courtroom near the judicial seats of Sarevok and the other Bhaalspawn."
  },
